{"tid":947762,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[你們的女神] 江嘉敏稱家教嚴唔敢講粗口 媽媽教揀男友要小心","createTime":"2018-12-19T13:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T18:49:55.000Z","uid":12558,"like":9,"dislike":405,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"1b43544d161f8c1799f97bf68db8c6e65551bd61","tid":947762,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T13:33:50.000Z","msg":"伍允龍、江嘉敏與電視劇《兄弟》多名演員到尖沙嘴街頭宣傳期間，江嘉敏被伍允龍大爆是打遊戲機高手，被問到可有膽挑戰張曦雯？江嘉敏說：「她是打電腦遊戲及PS4，而我則是打手機遊戲呢！不過也可以練習一下才挑戰，（但跟她打機要爆粗？）那可以一個中文、一個英文。哈哈！（你夠膽爆粗嗎？）暫時沒有這勇氣，真的不敢。」她解釋，因為家只有3個女兒，所以媽媽家教很嚴，她試過講了跟粗口同音的字已被媽媽「飛筷子」。<br />\n<br />\n那媽媽可有不准拍拖？江嘉敏則稱，自己已大個女了，媽媽沒有說不准，只要我小心點。被追問她是否要你小心點避孕？她尷地說：「要我小心點揀男友，未去到那麼進取的下一步，想找到對的才認真拍拖而不想玩。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ud1aV7x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fud1aV7x.png&h=179c3384&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZmTpf7y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZmTpf7y.png&h=702977f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff734794f9558c5a04fb590462962e15a5d6b227","tid":947762,"uid":38904,"like":284,"dislike":0,"score":284,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T13:37:32.000Z","msg":"tvb件衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800x533-fp/s3/media/image/2016/05/15/20160515-102918_U720_M156735_8eb7.jpg?itok=gCILznlS\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800x533-fp%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2016%2F05%2F15%2F20160515-102918_U720_M156735_8eb7.jpg%3Fitok%3DgCILznlS&h=66a6327e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc1d92801520f10f50ef5015f81d052ea71a32de","tid":947762,"uid":9004,"like":346,"dislike":5,"score":341,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T13:39:46.000Z","msg":"真係好撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa86895b9ea5f4b0a7d6c7254e4c9f1854e7494b","tid":947762,"uid":38519,"like":597,"dislike":4,"score":593,"citedB